## ---------------------------------------------------------------------
## 1. .NET / C# Project Build Overrides (compiler & AdminApp)
## ---------------------------------------------------------------------
# Ignore compilation artifacts, obj configurations, and intermediate binaries
**/bin/
**/obj/

# Avoid tracking auto-generated hot reload metadata files
.vs/
.vscode/
*.user
*.suo
*.userosscache
*.sln.docstates

## ---------------------------------------------------------------------
## 2. Web / Frontend Runtime & Environment Exclusions
## ---------------------------------------------------------------------
# Ignore local Node or bundler modules if you happen to run frontend utilities
node_modules/
.npm/

# Ignore local browser logging or runtime memory dumps
*.log
.eslintcache

## ---------------------------------------------------------------------
## 3. Architecture Rules - TRACK DATA & LAYOUTS, IGNORE GENERATED OUTPUTS
## ---------------------------------------------------------------------
# Allow tracking of your Git database folder structures (DO NOT IGNORE THESE)
!content/
!content/blog/
!content/blog/posts/
!content/guides.json
!templates/

# Optional Security Guardrail:
# If you ever save local raw secrets or API settings files in your app 
# instead of browser localStorage, keep them out of GitHub:
appsettings.Development.json
*.secrets.json